   <concept id="FAR_37_302" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">37.302</ph> Bonds or other security.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d2413e8" class="- topic/p ">When a contract is solely for dismantling, demolition, or removal of improvements,<xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid%3AUSC-prelim-title40-chapter31&amp;saved=%7CZ3JhbnVsZWlkOlVTQy1wcmVsaW0tdGl0bGU0MC1jaGFwdGVyMzctZnJvbnQ%3D%7C%7C%7C0%7Cfalse%7Cprelim&amp;edition=prelim"
                  scope="external"
                  format="html">40 U.S.C. chapter 31</xref>, subchapter III, Bonds, (see <xref href="28.102.dita#FAR_28_102"
                  base="i1088557"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">28.102</xref>) does not apply. However, the contracting officer may require the contractor to furnish a performance bond or other security (see <xref href="28.103.dita#FAR_28_103"
                  base="i1088629"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">28.103</xref>) in an amount that the contracting officer considers adequate to-</p>
         <ol id="d2386e34" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2408e21">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            Ensure completion of the work;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2408e26">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            Protect property to be retained by the Government;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2408e31">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
						            Protect property to be provided as compensation to the contractor; and</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2408e36">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
						            Protect the Government against damage to adjoining property.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
</dita>
